Package pl.put.poznan.transformer.storage

Class TransformsManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.put.poznan.transformer.storage.TransformsManager
  • public class TransformsManager
extends Object
    This class is a storage container and manager for TransformsResource objects. The storage is initialized on the beginning of execution and preserves the stored values until termination.
